  "texts": [
    "Table 2 gives a summary of accuracy measures used for colarado dataset.",
    "The scores for Root mean squared error (RMSE), MAE, and MAPE are 3227.79, 2885.26, and 0.25, respectively.",
    "As opposed to the ARMA model, the ARIMA model produced more accurate predictions after evaluating the data, with lower RMSE, MAE, and MAPE scores.",
    "However, testing with the SARIMA model produced the most encouraging findings since it is very accurate and correctly caught the increasing trend.",
    "This model's RMSE, MAE, and MAPE scores are much lower than those from the other models (1869.13, 1572, and 0.16, respectively)."
  ]
